snippet.title: Super Mario Universe - New Trailer
snippet.description:
SUPER MARIO UNIVERSE | New Trailer

Yo, Super Mario Universe is now in development since a few months and our progress is very well, so we made a new trailer for the mod in the last few days.
As you can obviously see, nearly everything has changed since the first trailer of the mod because we were very unhappy with the first trailer.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Credits:

A HACK BY TEAM UNIVERSE

- Level Design: Davetendo, Teltix
- Custom Tilesets: Rimea, iHarv, Baron, Dr. Yoshi
- Custom Music: NinTyler
- Soundtrack: Nintendo, NinTyler
- Custom Backgrounds: WillyMaker, Teltix, Boom69
- Tools: AboodXD, KillzXGaming
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Links:

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6JBY0Sp0AG9nYk_NCHo_aQ

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The trailer was made by Leon:
Discord : xLeonFyx#5237
